dct_title_s: PLAN of MUSCAT COVE and MUTRAH HARBOUR : Surveyed in 1785
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:21 000 (E 58°33'13"--E 58°38'42"/N 23°39'03"--N 23°36'06"). Oriented with west at the top. Nautical chart of Muscat Cove and Mutrah Harbour, showing depth soundings; bearings from fixed points listed below title. Includes inset 'View of MUTRAH from 20 fathoms on the Plan B'.
Ames Library of South Asia Maps
